                <h3 class="subheading">Key Features: Technology Meets Tradition</h3>
                <p>The Norton V4 is set to be a showcase of premium componentry and advanced rider aids. It will blend the classic craftsmanship of a TIG-welded, mirror-polished frame with the latest in performance technology.</p>
