                <p>The new V4, with its expected sharper aesthetics and powerful, Euro-5+ compliant engine, promises to be a highly sought-after machine. It’s a motorcycle for the enthusiast who values heritage and hand-built quality as much as they do lap times and cutting-edge electronics. This machine is poised to write the next illustrious chapter in Norton's long and storied history.</p>
